Description: Speed Limit: Divisible by 5, and < 90 OR = 999
Counter Peak Lanes: NULL if FACILITY_TYPE is 1
Single Unit / Combination: SU AADT + CU AADT < (0.8*AADT)
Median Width: NULL if (FACILITY_TYPE is 1 or 4) or Median_Type Code <2
Widening_Obstacle: Should contain A-G where Widening_Potential <9
DIR_Factor: DIR_Factor must be 100 where Facility_Type = 1
DIR_Factor: DIR_Factor must be 50=< and <=70 where Facility_Type = 2
Cracking_Percent: Should be < 75 where Surface Type is in (3,4,5,9,10)
Left Shoulder Width: Should be < Median_Width
Cracking_Percent: Should be < X where Surface Type is in (2,6,7,8)
Signal_Type: should = 5 or Null where F_System = 1 and Urban Code <> 99999
